---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — parry"
  description="parry's terms of service. Read about the rules and guidelines for using the parry app."
  canonicalPath="/terms"
>
  <section class="px-6 py-20 md:px-10 md:py-28 lg:px-14">
    <div class="prose-legal mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-5">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-display mb-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-5xl" style="letter-spacing: -0.025em;">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="mb-12 text-sm text-text-tertiary">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms of Service ("Terms") are an agreement between you and Anomaly Labs LLC ("we", "our", "us"), the operator of parry. By downloading, installing, or using parry ("the App" or "the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the Service.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p>
        parry is an AI-powered mobile application that generates message response suggestions. The app uses artificial intelligence to analyze input text and images and provide response options.
      </p>

      <h2>3. AI Data Processing and Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        parry uses artificial intelligence (specifically Anthropic's Claude AI) to generate message reply suggestions. When you submit text or images to parry, this content is sent to Anthropic's servers for AI processing. Anthropic retains this data for up to 7 days for safety monitoring purposes, after which it is automatically deleted. Your data is never used to train AI models.
      </p>
      <p>
        For more information about how Anthropic handles data, see <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Anthropic's Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Use of the Service</h2>
      <p>You agree to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the app only for lawful purposes</li>
        <li>Not use the app to harass, abuse, or harm others</li>
        <li>Not attempt to circumvent security features</li>
        <li>Not use the app to generate illegal, harmful, or inappropriate content</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. AI-Generated Content</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Responses are generated by AI and may not always be appropriate</li>
        <li>You are responsible for reviewing and editing responses before sending</li>
        <li>We do not guarantee the accuracy or appropriateness of AI-generated content</li>
        <li>You should not rely on AI suggestions for critical communications</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>User Responsibility</h3>
      <p>
        Reply suggestions generated by the Service are created by artificial intelligence and are provided for informational purposes only. You are solely responsible for reviewing, editing, and deciding whether to use any AI-generated suggestion. By sending a message based on an AI suggestion, you assume full responsibility for that message and its consequences.
      </p>

      <h3>No Professional Advice</h3>
      <p>
        parry does not provide legal, medical, financial, therapeutic, or any other form of professional advice. AI-generated suggestions should not be used as a substitute for professional judgment. If you need professional advice, consult a qualified professional.
      </p>

      <h3>Output Non-Uniqueness</h3>
      <p>
        AI-generated suggestions are not unique to you. Other users providing similar input may receive the same or substantially similar suggestions. You should not expect exclusivity over any AI-generated content.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Subscriptions and Payments</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Free tier: Limited daily generations</li>
        <li>Pro subscription: Increased daily generation limit and additional features</li>
        <li>Subscriptions are billed through Apple App Store or Google Play</li>
        <li>Subscription terms are governed by the respective app store</li>
        <li>Refunds are handled by the app store according to their policies</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>7. Cancellation</h2>
      <p>You may cancel your subscription at any time through:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>iOS:</strong> Settings &gt; [Your Name] &gt; Subscriptions</li>
        <li><strong>Android:</strong> Play Store &gt; Subscriptions</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period.</p>

