      <p>
        Before filing any formal claim, you agree to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@parryai.app">support@parryai.app</a> and attempt to resolve the dispute informally for at least 30 days.
      </p>

      <h3>Binding Arbitration</h3>
      <p>
        If we cannot resolve a dispute informally, any dispute, claim, or controversy arising out of or relating to these Terms or the Service shall be resolved by binding individual arbitration administered by the American Arbitration Association ("AAA") in accordance with its Consumer Arbitration Rules. Arbitration shall take place in Washington, United States. The arbitrator's decision shall be final and binding and may be entered as a judgment in any court of competent jurisdiction.
